Usage: set_mode [-help] <list_of_modes> <object_list> [-type {cell}]

-help            # Prints out the command usage
<list_of_modes>  # Specifies the name(s) of library mode value
                 # (string, required)
<object_list>    # List of instances (string, required)
-type {cell}     # Specifies the library mode at instance level
                 # (enum, optional)